rComments: Most boring and annoying prof ever. She is a caring old woman which is nice, but does not teach anything of real relevance during lecture. The course is entirely dependent on the huge textbook, and you have to pretty much know every thing in it to do well on the exam. TAs are unnecessarily tough graders and are hard to please. Not a bird course.

Extremely sweet professor! The course consists of a few papers worth 15-20% each and a final exam in which she gives a list of what to study. Was my easiest course of 1st semester because you're dealing with concepts that are talked about in tutorials instead of memorization. Sometimes cool guests would be brought in too! recommend.

The readings are really simple and mostly talk of experiences of others. Prof is nice but lecs can be a bit boring. Brings in guest speakers. The TA Preeia is really good at explaining things. Prof shows interesting vids and talks about current events happening. She's nice enough.
She's a bit disorganized but overall a great professor.

One of the worst Professors I've ever encountered. She has a hard time seeing past her 2nd wave feminist lens and completely disrespects her students as infants. Ironic to the oppression she teaches against, she actually is a source of oppression for students in her classroom. I had such a horrible experience taking her classes.

She was a great prof, pretty much gave us the questions to the exam and made sure we were well prepared. Very helpful and clearly wants the best for her students. Assignments were easy and straight forward. Overall great prof, I would take a class with her again.

This prof is so difficult to consult with. She isn't clear on what is on the final and we never know what grade we have because of no midterm and late handing back the assignments. She can be really demeaning as well. Her lectures are mostly discussion, and barely discuss the readings. She teaches C02 as well. NOT taking that!
